data.description: Spacious 3 Level Townhouse in sought after LaPlata, Maryland.  3 Bedrooms/3 Full Baths/1 Half Bath with a Finished Basement has plenty of space for a growing family.  New Windows, Heating/A/C System and Roof are all less than 5 years old.  The kitchen was remodeled with new cabinets, mosaic back flash and stainless steel appliances less than 5 years ago.  The Finished Basement has laminated floors and includes space for Family Room and/or Office along with a Full Bath.   The Electric Fireplace installed in the basement less than  3 years ago.  Deck and Fenced-In Yard in rear of property.  This lovely townhouse is just waiting for your personal touch.   Short Sale/SOLD Strictly “AS IS”.
